<p><a id="TSJN-01-04-0856-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to Your excellency's inquiry in text" href="#TSJN-01-04-0856-ks-0001">Your excellencys inquiry</a>: <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-04-02-0683" class="document">TJ to Hunter, 7 Feb. 1781</a>. <a id="TSJN-01-04-0856-kw-0002" class="keywordref" title="jump to The writers employed there in text" href="#TSJN-01-04-0856-ks-0002">The writers employed there</a>: By writers Hunter must have meant clerks; see <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Calendar of Virginia State Papers  Preserved in the Capitol at Richmond&lt;/i&gt; ]">CVSP</span>, <span class="hi-small-caps" style="font-variant: small-caps;">i</span>, 531.</p></div>
